        public PwMockLocationProvider(android.content.Context context,
                      java.lang.String jsonFileName,
                      boolean repeat,
                      PwMockLocationProvider.MockLocationsDisabledListener listener)
        Creates a PwMockLocationProvider
        Parameters:
        context - The application context object
        jsonFileName - The name and path of the json file to be used for location data. Starting after "assets/"
        repeat - True if the points in the JSON file should repeat indefinitely; false if the list of points should only be shown once
        listener - The listener that will handle notifying the user that mock locations need to be enabled in the device settings
